{
  "stem": "14002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But I couldn't find any work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And not long after that, I came back to Novoselica.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "As I came back-- and, of course, I didn't go to school, because I wasn't allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So they took me, also, what they called munkatabor, but not as-- as military, because I was still young.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There was a forest not far from us, where I had to go there and work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We're cutting wood and put it on the train-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] to put it on the train and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I was working there for over a year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Of course, I never got paid for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "The only thing, by the end of the week, what they used to give us, was flour and-- and-- should I-- and ham.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Of course, I'm religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We are religious at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We wouldn't use that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "What I used to do, I used to bring that ham to a gentile in a store.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "He used to give me flour for the ham.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "This is how-- this is how it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "When that ended, I started to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "There were one fellow, in the next town, in Neresnytsya they called it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "He was from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "When Hitler came to power, he ran away from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I started to work for him, just to-- just to pass time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I was bored.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was at that age, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, my mother was home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One sister was, by-- by the end, in Teresva.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So basically, it was my brother, Chaim, and Golda, what they were home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was up to 1944. 1944, when Hitler-- when Hitler took over Hungary, my-- that was before Pesach.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
